Bullet_train_collision_in_Zhejiang
Video taken just before train crash
2011-07-28 07:54:17 GMT
This mobile phone video was taken by a passenger named Wang Hairu, who sat in the No. 16 carriage of the D3315 bullet train, which was hit in the rear end by the D301 bullet train just five minutes after the video was recorded on July 23, 2011.In the video, the last passenger to be rescued from the wreckage, two-year-old Yiyi who happened to be seated close to Wang Hairu with her mother and two other relatives, could be heard calling to her mom.
